Time sped swiftly on its wings of pleasure; the last article was plucked from the tree, and the waning tapers began to drop like tiny meteors from its branches. The last merry game was played, and the youthful revelers showed need of 

Tired nature's sweet restorer, balmy sleep;
                   and with cheerful "good nights," and many kind words and good wishes for future happiness and prosperity, the gay party dispersed.
